{{see|Xe}}
==English==
{{wikipediapar|xe (pronoun)}}
===Etymology===
Attributed to [[w:Jim Sinclair|Jim Sinclair]], who apparently coined it a. 1992.

===Pronoun===
'''xe''' 
# ''(chiefly Internet)'' That person; a subject-case gender-neutral pronoun.

===Declension===
* Subject: '''xe'''
* Object:  [[xem]]
* Possessive: [[xyr]] or [[xir]] (or [[hir]])
* Reflexive: [[xyrself]] or [[xirself]] (perhaps rarely [[xemself]])

===See also===
* [[hir]]

